{"tid":1586363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非入！我話你知點保護勇武！","createTime":"2019-09-22T02:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T02:03:15.000Z","uid":201178,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a9315fef59f331f575480af6b7745d51a2226718","tid":1586363,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"屌 眼見個女仔同班狗講「係咪一閃一閃小星星」就比人話臭雞真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想同個女仔講 你做得好好！<br />\n同時諗到新宣傳方向：比狗鬧既和理非直接向鏡頭講班狗點人身攻擊你！！！<br />\n<br />\n班狗幾低EQ就係香港人都知，<br />\n但臭雞、想搵黑社會斬撚死你呢咁既言論<br />\n去到國際真係好爆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔好唔記得警察係代表緊個政府</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由受害者自己對鏡頭講發生咩事，係一個對外界最直接既求助！<br />\n1.搵一個鏡頭，最好外國佬<br />\n2.將件事連帶憤怒由頭到尾簡單講一次<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（英文好就用英文）</span><br />\n3.反屋企休息</span></span><br />\n手足同國際會幫你煲大佢！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小呢件事，呢刻，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會係將班狗既暴行正式放上國際既一刻！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非們，你地既力量唔會比勇武少，<br />\n只要黑警黑出國際，有壓力，佢地自然會打人都細力啲，<br />\n呢刻，亦係和理非保護勇武既一刻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港黑警，我要你黑出國際<br />\n生生世世留係大灣區</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Mon post狗，如果你睇緊呢個post，<br />\n請你spread開比你班狗仔同事，一齊train下EQ，<br />\n國際版老竇搵仔，都唔係好難。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Q：我個樣係咪會揚左？<br />\nA：和理非既好處就係永遠企係道德高地。無野好怕。再者，當你比狗人身攻擊既時候媒體同班狗既cam都已經影左你。<br />\n<br />\nQ：唔直接講都有媒體影到啦，點解要我講？<br />\nA：由當事人講出黎說服力會強好多。唔單係傳播緊件事，仲係向國際叫緊救命。<br />\n<br />\nQ：點解要即刻講？<br />\nA：感情。遊說人感情好重要，記住，咁做既目的係借媒體支鏡大聲叫救命。感情愈強烈，愈震撼。<br />\n<br />\nQ：我講咩好？<br />\nA：將自己想講既講曬出黎就夠。建議30秒內講完。<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"19744774f4eaf6ce78fa0233a03e75e0ee5a1c2a","tid":1586363,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae75ea1101bf093a523c6ee775f7273063755204","tid":1586363,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6bc3f50dc39d9f7ebd48d23d50f82ce6ae20dc","tid":1586363,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7449e6a5c4c9342075a377a4233627c032da14b","tid":1586363,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b84da3ba33aff4e09f3cdf761ac1c59edcf2d0","tid":1586363,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"<im